    | Module Hooks
  dl#module-loader-hooks.dl-horizontal
    dt preResources
    dd
      p Is triggered directly before resources (files) are loaded for all modules using the ModuleLoader.
    dt configureApp
    dd
      p Is triggered after all resources (files) have loaded but before any routes have been attached.
    dt preRoute
    dd
      p Is triggered directly before routes are initialized for all modules being loaded.

